# =============================================================
# World App Ruleset for Loon
#
# Description: Redirects all traffic for the World App,
# developed by Tools for Humanity, to a specific proxy.
#
# Author: Gemini
# Last Updated: 2025-08-20
# =============================================================

# Part 1: Core Project & App Domains
# 核心项目及应用域名
# Covers the main websites and backend services for World App and Worldcoin.
# 涵盖 World App 和 Worldcoin 项目的主要网站及后端服务。
DOMAIN-SUFFIX, world.org
DOMAIN-SUFFIX, worldcoin.org
DOMAIN-SUFFIX, toolsforhumanity.com

# Part 2: Third-Party Services
# 第三方服务
# Includes domains for analytics, monitoring, and other services used by the app.
# 包含应用所使用的分析、监控等服务的域名。
DOMAIN-SUFFIX, datadoghq.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX, world-id-assets.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX, pactsafe.io

# Part 3: General Keyword-based Catch-all
# 基于关键词的通用规则
# A fallback to catch any other subdomains or related services.
# 用于捕获任何其他子域名或相关服务的备用规则。
DOMAIN-KEYWORD, worldcoin
DOMAIN-KEYWORD, worldapp


